 * This component is used for displaying the amount input UI to user in Durian On-ramp flow.
 * This component is very similar to the AmountInput CDS component.
 * However, it has some major differences due to the different use case of Durian on-ramp flow:
 * - Does not require a `Wallet` instance passed as prop
 * - Currency toggle button can be disabled
 * - Different tertiary text
 *
